metadata.name: God Hates Neon #1/5
metadata.description:
God Hates Neon is a collection of digitally created NFTs made through refinement of existing artworks released to the GHNFT community, as well as future hired artist(s) and/or artist collaborations, all are available on the Ethereum blockchain. 

With ALL proceeds and future commissions, I vow to sweep the floor(s) of GodHatesNFTees & associated projects (ApeHatersClub, etc.) as well as continued minting, everything will be held in a fully transparent wallet (godhatesneon.eth)
